":"44a608c648b1d554e06afaa9bcf0396878198959","tid":1380233,"uid":177759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"香港都想攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703faecccf96f8545bdd881b2ba39c25a45e483f","tid":1380233,"uid":37443,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:20:37.000Z","msg":"嚴格黎講係港共要同香港攬炒<br />\n成地係好撚驚俾中共清算<br />\n因為佢地咁多年黎挑撥離間兩地關係<br />\n用撚左咁多維穩費<br />\n冇改善不突止 重要決裂呢種地步<br />\n即係佢地既工作係錯<br />\n<br />\n而今次終於爆煲啦<br />\n所以港共政權其實都係冇後路 <br />\n決心同香港攬炒"},{"pid":"0e2ab017501a5270db882f9af7112bc3dc050624","tid":1380233,"uid":231102,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"c45ed891dcca2a586894dd24032f1c728936528b","tid":1380233,"uid":106929,"like":124,"dislike":1,"score":123,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:26:03.000Z","msg":"其實大家都好想攬炒  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:22:18.000Z","msg":"weconnect，至少大家喺攬炒方面有共同理念"},{"pid":"b90c916d6910f9d04c89addf0557fdd0f2975c60","tid":1380233,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f800f57c1a13852f3b2e18e03828d3e5d62adbad","tid":1380233,"uid":209248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等睇攬炒 邊個傷d"},{"pid":"2748b30e49de18e5b474b3e7420e0c4291cdf1a9","tid":1380233,"uid":37796,"like":6,"dislike":71,"score":-65,"quote":{"pid":"ddf1103edc6a6f53b704a70d9b78f7d7e4447524","tid":1380233,"uid":2419,"like":244,"dislike":3,"score":241,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:25:50.000Z","msg":"連登批評佢既只係五毛 <br />\n<br />\n幾日前開始有一堆人鬧佢<br />\n<br />\n希望有識佢既人講返俾佢知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"劉細良根本係另類大台，正宗冷氣軍師<br /